/glare <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ukbern.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kbern</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#3333cc>Drinalese</font></span><br>  Posts: 318<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/3/02 9:45:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=820.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ....</span><hr size=1> I felt bad for Draper after that hit because of the damage done.<br>
<br>
That being said there have been much more malicious hits on players that receive no penalties.<br>
<br>
Claude is a mean player but I dont think even he wanted Draper to be smeared like that.<br>
<br>
